      <title>SSR一键脚本</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/18/SSR%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/18/SSR%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="老生常谈第一步进入root模式"><a href="#老生常谈第一步进入root模式" class="headerlink" title="老生常谈第一步进入root模式"></a>老生常谈第一步进入root模式</h1><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo -i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h1 id="2-安装bbr-plus"><a href="#2-安装bbr-plus" class="headerlink" title="2.安装bbr plus"></a>2.安装bbr plus</h1><blockquote><p>不会的看我上一篇文章 </p></blockquote><h1 id="3-安装ssr"><a href="#3-安装ssr" class="headerlink" title="3.安装ssr"></a>3.安装ssr</h1><h2 id="3-1-下载ssr"><a href="#3-1-下载ssr" class="headerlink" title="3.1 下载ssr"></a>3.1 下载ssr</h2><hr><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget --no-check-certificate https:&#x2F;&#x2F;raw.githubusercontent.com&#x2F;teddysun&#x2F;shadowsocks_install&#x2F;master&#x2F;shadowsocksR.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x shadowsocksR.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="3-2-运行安装"><a href="#3-2-运行安装" class="headerlink" title="3.2 运行安装"></a>3.2 运行安装</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.&#x2F;shadowsocksR.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><a href="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.1.md.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="2.1.md.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="2.1.md.png" data-src="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.1.md.png" class="lazyload" title="2.1.md.png"></a>]</p><h2 id="3-3-配置"><a href="#3-3-配置" class="headerlink" title="3.3 配置"></a>3.3 配置</h2><p><strong>配置密码配置协议，加密方式，混淆</strong></p><p><a href="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.2.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt data-src="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.2.png" class="lazyload" title></a></p><p><strong>安装中红色报错不用管</strong></p><p><a href="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.3.md.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt data-src="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.3.md.png" class="lazyload" title></a></p><h2 id="3-4-配置完成，下载客户端输入即可科学上网"><a href="#3-4-配置完成，下载客户端输入即可科学上网" class="headerlink" title="3.4 配置完成，下载客户端输入即可科学上网"></a>3.4 配置完成，下载客户端输入即可科学上网</h2><p><a href="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.4.md.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt data-src="http://photo.xmhcool.xyz/images/2020/02/18/2.4.md.png" class="lazyload" title></a></p>]]></content>
      
      
